snippet.title: Official Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag PlayStation Exclusive Content Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a first look at the Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag gameplay coming exclusive to PlayStation®3 and PlayStation®4.

Rated Mature: Blood, sexual themes, strong language, use of alcohol, and violence.
